Working in small, nimble teams you'll be supporting and enhancing our Platform
that underpins all of our enterprise applications. You'll be developing
insanely great, market leading solutions that delight and amaze, transform
business and make life simple for our customers.  
  
You'll be joining a high performing team, that has many opportunities for long
term career development, whether you want to go down the individual
contributor path or move into team leadership, the future of your career is in
your hands.  
  
As a Developer at TechnologyOne you'll challenge conventional thinking, think
outside the square and go beyond the traditional realms of development.  
  
  

##  ** What you'll be doing… **

  * Writing simple, elegant code to develop a robust core automation and orchestration platform that provides a stable and elegant experience for our teams 
  * Developing a deep and 'hands on' understanding of the product: its features, functions, design and architecture to develop amazing code 
  * Working with the System Architect and Business Analyst to assist in designing software that exceeds expectations 
  * Delivering exceptional bug free software to meet the defined KPIs for software quality and performance and managing the delivery to agreed timeframes 
  * Personally using and testing the software as it is being built to ensure it is of the highest quality and insanely great 
  * Performing thorough analysis on business problems to develop smart solutions that make life simple for our customers 

##  ** Your Talents… **

  * A passion for technology and software development along with an eagerness to delve into any problem 
  * Solid software developments skills in.Net C#, Microservices, 
  * Experience in building platforms in Linux, Docker and git 
  * Knowledge and understanding of technologies such as AWS, Kubernetes, Terraform are nice to have. 
  * Additional points if you have experience with: Camunda/Xeebe, Jenkins, Dapr, CDKTF and gRPC 
  * Experience with enterprise or large systems development is advantageous 

##  ** Benefits… **

  * Competitive remuneration package. 
  * Free gym access on site 
  * Free breakfast and coffee on-site. 
  * Industry leading Employee Share Plan. 
  * More free event T-shirts than you will ever need. 
  * Amazing Culture? 
  * Premium new office fit out with excellent facilities 
  * Additional 2.5 days of annual leave dedicated to volunteering through our Foundation with some of our wonderful charity partners. 
  * Defined career framework - know what options you have in your career path and how you can get there. 

_ TechnologyOne is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer who values
diversity and an inclusive workplace. We aim to recruit a diverse range of
people with a diverse range of talents to help us to deliver on our mission to
better our community. _ _ If you meet a number of the requirements (and not
all), we encourage you to submit your application. _  

##  ** Who we are… **

TechnologyOne (ASX: TNE) is Australia's largest enterprise software company
and one of Australia's top 100 ASX-listed companies, with locations across six
countries. We provide a global SaaS ERP solution that transforms business and
makes life simple for our customers. Our deeply integrated enterprise SaaS
solution is available on any device, anywhere and anytime and is incredibly
easy to use. Over 1,200 leading corporations, government agencies, local
councils and universities are powered by our software.  
  
For more than 36 years, we have been providing our customers enterprise
software that evolves and adapts to new and emerging technologies, allowing
them to focus on their business and not technology.

